00:59:17,512 --> 00:59:19,889
Thus, the court sentences him
to two years…

777
00:59:22,475 --> 00:59:23,935
Defendant. Are you all right?

778
00:59:29,732 --> 00:59:30,775
Defendant.

779
00:59:36,781 --> 00:59:38,491
Defendant! Defendant!

780
00:59:38,575 --> 00:59:39,784
Please check on him.

781
00:59:41,786 --> 00:59:43,454
Mr. Park Kitae. Can you hear me?

782
00:59:43,538 --> 00:59:45,248
Defendant! Mr. Park Kitae!

783
00:59:49,752 --> 00:59:52,297
-There is no heartbeat.
-What in the world…

784
00:59:52,380 --> 00:59:54,257
AED! Please bring a defibrillator now.

785
00:59:54,340 --> 00:59:55,258
Yes, Your Honor.

786
01:00:22,619 --> 01:00:24,120
What's going on? Why isn't it working?

787
01:00:24,203 --> 01:00:25,413
Dang.

788
01:00:26,914 --> 01:00:28,916
-What about the ambulance?
-I called for it already.

789
01:00:34,380 --> 01:00:36,341
-Is he dead?
-There is no hope.

790
01:00:36,424 --> 01:00:39,093
Too much time has passed.

791
01:00:52,732 --> 01:00:53,941
Han Yihan.

792
01:00:57,695 --> 01:00:59,280
What on earth are you doing here?

793
01:01:45,868 --> 01:01:47,912
WE THANK NAM KEEAE AND LEE YUNHUI
FOR SPECIAL APPEARANCES

794
01:01:52,834 --> 01:01:55,253
<i>To be honest, I am surprised.
I didn't expect such a change.</i>

795
01:01:55,336 --> 01:01:57,922
<i>Why are you surprised?
Did you think I would be gone forever?</i>

796
01:01:58,005 --> 01:01:59,882
You made a promise that night.

797
01:01:59,966 --> 01:02:01,467
<i>You will uphold that promise.</i>

798
01:02:01,551 --> 01:02:03,052
<i>A lawyer? How could you defend</i>

799
01:02:03,136 --> 01:02:05,930
a doctor
from Banseok University Medical Center?

800
01:02:06,013 --> 01:02:07,056
<i>Let's keep this professional.</i>

801
01:02:07,140 --> 01:02:10,268
<i>We are only a prosecutor and a lawyer
who met for a trial.</i>

802
01:02:10,351 --> 01:02:14,105
<i>Banseok University Medical Center
received approval to proceed Phase Two.</i>

803
01:02:14,397 --> 01:02:16,566
<i>Honours Hand? A lobbyist?</i>

804
01:02:16,649 --> 01:02:19,777
<i>It's where people
with a demon's tongue and fingers gather.</i>

805
01:02:19,861 --> 01:02:21,446
I am the black-haired foreigner
who works there.

806
01:02:21,529 --> 01:02:24,657
I am the head of the Asian branch,
Jayden Lee.

807
01:02:25,158 --> 01:02:26,159
Let's be on good terms.

808
01:02:26,242 --> 01:02:27,368
<i>We will be.</i>

809
01:02:30,663 --> 01:02:32,665
Translated by Won-hyang Son
